kernel config for usb and bluetooth
1. Networking support ---> Bluetooth subsystem support ---> all
2. Device drivers ---> Input device support ---> Joystick interface
											---> Joysticks/Gamepads
				  ---> HID devices ---> /dev/hidraw raw HID device support
				  				   ---> USB human interface device (full HID) support
				  				   ---> /dev/hidraw raw HID device support 
				  				   ---> Special HID drivers ---> Sony PS3 controller			
				  ---> USB support ---> USB device filesystem
				  				   ---> USB device class-devices
				  				   ---> EHCI HCD (USB 2.0) support
				  				   ---> USB serial converter support ---> USB generic serial driver
				  				   									 ---> USB cp210x family of UART bridge driver  